{"tid":2026866,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"要光復粵語，首先唔好特登改一個英文名，要改用粵音英文名","createTime":"2020-05-21T08:28:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T11:14:32.000Z","uid":241093,"like":22,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b28b8464b5bdb49894dd04d0f93fac4309687f20","tid":2026866,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:28:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">利伸先：並非反洋</span><br />\n<br />\n只係唔明點解香港人個英文名，要係特登去「改」<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明明身分證嘅「粵音英文名」<br />\n一早就係你嘅英文名</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n乜嘢Alan, ben, cathy 嗰啲<br />\n大部分人身分證都冇呢啲洋名 <br />\n如果想粵語更加發揚光大 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">更加應該以自己嘅粵音英文名為傲 唔應該矮化佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">陳小明 Chan Siu Ming (英文名: Siuming) <br />\n李大豪 Lee Dai Ho (英文名： Daiho)<br />\n林美麗 Lam Mei Lai (英文名：Meilai) </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同樣亞洲人 都冇香港人咁多特意改洋名<br />\n大多係跟返自己語言嘅「英文名」：<br />\n<br />\n(括號為外界的稱呼)<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n本田圭佑 - Honda Keisuke (Honda)<br />\n新垣結衣 - Aragaki Yui (Aragaki)<br />\n孫興慜 - Son Heung min (Son)<br />\n金泰妍 Kim  Tae Yeon(TaeYeon)</span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，首先光復粵語，唔應該矮化佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認同樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔認同樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a20f59d4e0407fb6f35e10bff125992348df26","tid":2026866,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:31:15.000Z","msg":"但好柒"},{"pid":"9a2c5b8705796d0f0e58663bfba9e66fff95f39b","tid":2026866,"uid":33618,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:34:53.000Z","msg":"香港係國際大都會(雖然好快變直轄市)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個人都應該有個英文名囉唔該"},{"pid":"bbefb61b45501ea60cd08442511ca086ad9e4a63","tid":2026866,"uid":71237,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:35:34.000Z","msg":"認同，講得幾好<br />\n火影忍者角色啲名全部係拼音，啲鬼佬睇嗰陣都無障礙<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Naruto_characters\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FList_of_Naruto_characters&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsb1zpTq0bGO0w7tnLPpoXkc%3D&h=8b237dce\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Naruto_characters</a>"},{"pid":"fb8dabaa48a012ee21593b941bd572e1671f9b2e","tid":2026866,"uid":241093,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9a2c5b8705796d0f0e58663bfba9e66fff95f39b","tid":2026866,"uid":33618,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:34:53.000Z","msg":"香港係國際大都會(雖然好快變直轄市)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個人都應該有個英文名囉唔該"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:38:41.000Z","msg":"除非老豆老母一早幫你改洋名喺身分證上(Alan, Ben, Cathy)<br />\n<br />\n但如果冇，就唔使特登去改<br />\n用返你身分證上嘅粵音英文名就得喇<br />\n<br />\n利伸：本人就係例子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01c0651b0d7afccf9c42c09f45ff044c33ad018","tid":2026866,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:40:53.000Z","msg":"好多人叫阿Ling<br />\nMay<br />\nMan/Mandy"},{"pid":"0bfcb6bb0ded27bc55a16ba1b6025c5ae55f76de","tid":2026866,"uid":62802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:42:55.000Z","msg":"求幫推<br />\n[香港文化] 上連登打正字<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2026832\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2026832</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3325a98879003b9aa4fe31f88a8b1b30821cd862","tid":2026866,"uid":21699,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:43:24.000Z","msg":"而家長居外國<br />\n個英文名都係粵語拼音, 人地都係叫我粵語拼音個名<br />\n如果你細個有人幫你改英文名, 而你又用慣左, 你身份證上英文名都係呢個, 覺得好舒服, 對個名有sense of identity, 咁你用英文名係OK<br />\n<br />\n但如果你唔覺得個英文名係叫緊自己, 你passport 又冇呢個名 (住外國會好有好麻煩), 咁你都係用返粵語拚音吧啦<br />\n<br />\n香港大部分人都係後者"},{"pid":"8d5dc0988898c40e8f7ae76a06d2cb22b5b9f823","tid":2026866,"uid":54550,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:43:25.000Z","msg":"外國人係稱呼你個姓先...<br />\n夠close先會叫你個名...<br />\n就算你無洋名,熟左佢都係照叫你個名<br />\n當然再熟就會變啲nickname出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de33e3c5c3e54cd280353db19558244e48446928","tid":2026866,"uid":241093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bbefb61b45501ea60cd08442511ca086ad9e4a63","tid":2026866,"uid":71237,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:35:34.000Z","msg":"認同，講得幾好<br />\n火影忍者角色啲名全部係拼音，啲鬼佬睇嗰陣都無障礙<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Naruto_characters\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FList_of_Naruto_characters&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsb1zpTq0bGO0w7tnLPpoXkc%3D&h=8b237dce\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Naruto_characters</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:46:28.000Z","msg":"用返自己語言嘅拼音當英文名<br />\n其實都係間接嘅文化輸岀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f79845f7f658668b2fce315b76afa42640d8f77","tid":2026866,"uid":241093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3325a98879003b9aa4fe31f88a8b1b30821cd862","tid":2026866,"uid":21699,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:43:24.000Z","msg":"而家長居外國<br />\n個英文名都係粵語拼音, 人地都係叫我粵語拼音個名<br />\n如果你細個有人幫你改英文名, 而你又用慣左, 你身份證上英文名都係呢個, 覺得好舒服, 對個名有sense of identity, 咁你用英文名係OK<br />\n<br />\n但如果你唔覺得個英文名係叫緊自己, 你passport 又冇呢個名 (住外國會好有好麻煩), 咁你都係用返粵語拚音吧啦<br />\n<br />\n香港大部分人都係後者"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:52:33.000Z","msg":"係 <br />\n小學嗰陣英文老師迫我改英文名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我心諗呢個名同我都冇關聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中學就一直用粵語拼音當係英文名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然間唔中被人問點解冇英文名<br />\n但當其他人嗌你時 先感覺係叫緊自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18b07a4e06d1824d9bee97461719178f8165fec","tid":2026866,"uid":118346,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:57:00.000Z","msg":"My name is Kit  (傑). <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f14d53ae7ae010efbbfeb5d82208ddc16a809a","tid":2026866,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c18b07a4e06d1824d9bee97461719178f8165fec","tid":2026866,"uid":118346,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:57:00.000Z","msg":"My name is Kit  (傑). <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:58:21.000Z","msg":"My name is Son. (孫興慜)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa79dd9bd85ef212796dc064b97f8997c0ae1ffb","tid":2026866,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5da33d261918a3e87a0a86034bb2f41cb63cf6","tid":2026866,"uid":163865,"like":3,"dislike